6.2     Effect of Termination.  In the event of termination of this EULA You must destroy all copies of the Software.  In addition You must remove all copies of the Software, including all backup copies, from all computers and services on which it is installed.  From time to time, RightScale may change the terms of this EULA.  RightScale will notify You of such change.  Following such notification Your continued use of the Software will indicate Your agreement to the change.
